data.description: Lynnwood Neighborhood gem on the green space! Buyer rate buy down possible. Backyard privacy and wildlife viewing. Pond and large fenced yard. One of the largest homes in the neighborhood, 3 levels, huge rooms, 2+ windows in most rooms for amazing light. Huge garage. Fabulous hardwoods throughout, protected by years of carpet. Redwood siding. A great home for remote work, gatherings, privacy, lots of storage. New electrical panel 7-14-23 with 3 yr. transferable advantage plan, wired for generator. 2 furnaces serviced 9-1-23. New roof on 10-18-2023! Fully deep cleaned. Quiet yet close. Greenspace lot, overlooks CE Mason Wetlands Park, parks, schools, even walkable to the Patricia Reser Center and Beaverton Transit Center. Well built, well maintained home, only one family since build. An estate that leaves a blank slate for loving cosmetic touch in the next chapter.
